_sText:
Well this is my fist map release here in fpsbananna. Ive been making maps for a while now. Well as you can see this is a beta map, final map to come out soon. Map included 2 execution chamber, Shower Room, Hospital, Pool, Basketball, Soccer, and exterior Dock with Boat. Please comment on what you like and don't like and what you would like to see in the final version. Enjoy :-) 

Jail cells open after 40 seconds.
